t tho last dlsburse\nj ment of 20 cents and a 20-cent extra\nfailed to affect the stock. New Mux\nj 100 and Arizoful Land continued\nI strong, getting above 8.\n6 fit Serv 149 146% 146*4\n3 Ci\u00ab Serv pfd 71% 71*4 71%\n$2.C\u00abh\u00bb fit Sen C ecrlp.. 72 72 72\nSB,OOO Cit Serv *.-rlp 92 90 90\n5 Creole Synd 3% 8% 8%\n2 Derby II 4 It w i. 77 7\n1 Derby OAK pfd w| 30 30 30\n30 Engineers Pet 06 .06 .06\n10 Federal Oil 30 .30 .30\n1 (ten Pet 42*4 42*4 42%\n1 (ill Oil vtg tr cfs. 4 4 4\n5 Gulf OH of F\u00bb 61 60 60\n1 Golf St AR w I I*4 I*4 1%\n7 \\Mgo Pet tl 3 3\n5 Latin Amer 0i1... .95 .95 .95\n10 Lvn, Pet 26 .26 .26\n1 M\u00abrg\u00aby OH 1% 1% 1%\n15 Meg Fanu<\u2019u 95 .90 .95\n13 Mount Prod 17% 17 17\n2 Omar Oil A (tan.. .75 .75 .75\nNew Mex Land 8% 7% 7\u20194\n146 Mutual Oil vot cfa 12*4 12% 12%\n2N Y Oil 11% 11% 11%\n52 Penn Reaver Oil.. .62 .65 ,60\n3 IVnno.-k Oil 14% 14 14%\n10 Red Hunk Oil te w. 12 11% 12\n5 Roy Can Oil A Ref 3% 3*4 3%\nI Rynn on 4** 4% 4%\n3 Salt Ck Cons B*4 s', 8%\n9 Salt Ck Prod 21 20*;. 2u%\nIT Seals,aid Oil 1% 1% I\n1 Ti.lal Osage Oil 1* 11 14\n2U S Cities Oorp A 23% 23 23%\n10 Wilcox Oil A Gas. T 7% 7%\nINDUSTRIALS.\n3 Am I A Tract 129% 12S 128\n39 Atlantic Fruit wi. 2 2 2\nBurden A Co 119% 119% 119%\n3 Bril-Am Tub cou.. 21% 21% 21%\n5 Brlt-Aui Tub Co ti-j 21 \u20194 21\u2019, 21\u2019,\n22 Bklyn City R 1t.... 12% U-% 11%\n34 Caruly I\u2019r Corp wi 2% I\u20194 I\u2019,\n1 Chi Xlt tr new wi 20% 2<> 2 20*4\nUolurado Pow A I.t 22% 22% 22%\n1 Conti Tub Co 23 23 23\n6 Culm Co 38% 37 37\nDI,A W C oal 92 92 92\n12 DnblUer t: A Radio 2\"% li*'-4 20%\n6 Dunhill Inti Ine 25 25 25\nM Intrant Mot 29*4 28% 29\nIDu Pont Motors.. 2% 2*s 2%\n*4 Federal Light 71 71 71\n3F A iV Grand wl.. 43*-j 43% 43\u2019-\n*4 Gillette S R 237% 273 273%\n3 Glen A Men C0a1... 8-1 83% 83%\n15 Hazeitine Carp wl 15% 15 15\n3 Hav Tobaeeo pfd... 3% 3*4 3%\n9 Heyden Chen 2 I 2\n1 lliidsou Co pfd 18% 18% 18%\n%Me Co pfd 78% 78% 78%\n1 Inter Conti Rubber. 4 4 4\nj 1 Int